   	                            Generic DIO (BC059)
                            Scaler version feature list
                                  David M. Kline
                                February 26, 2008
===============================================================================
FEATURES:
    - 16 32bit scalers, up/dwn, enable/disable
    - Armout
    - Armin
    - Gatein
    - Grouping
    - Asyn-based Scaler record support
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
SUPPORTED HARDWARE:
V1.1.3
    ATH-DIO
    RMM-416
    OMM-DIO
    OMM-DIO-XT
V1.4
    ATH-DIO
    RMM-416
    OMM-DIO
    OMM-DIO-XT
    See GDIO_SCALER for connection information.

V2.0
    ATH-DIO
    RMM-416
    OMM-DIO
    OMM-DIO-XT
    See BC059_SCALER for connection information.
    See BC059_SCALER_V20LC for connection information.
        This descibes the FPGA instance employing the "Latch / Clear"
        functionality provided for Sector 12.

V2.1
    ATH-DIO
    RMM-416
    OMM-DIO
    OMM-DIO-XT
    See BC059_SCALER for connection information.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
